    <title>FEXO主题</title>
    <url>/2020/02/28/fexo-README/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Fexo"><a href="#Fexo" class="headerlink" title="Fexo"></a>Fexo</h1><blockquote>
<p>A minimalist design theme for Hexo.</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>一个极简主义设计的 Hexo 主题。</p>
</blockquote>
<p><a href="http://forsigner.com/" target="_blank">Demo</a><br>|<br><a href="http://forsigner.com/2016/03/10/fexo-doc-zh-cn/" target="_blank">文档</a><br>|<br><a href="http://forsigner.com/2016/03/10/fexo-doc-zh-tw/" target="_blank">文檔</a><br>|<br><a href="http://forsigner.com/2016/03/10/fexo-doc-en/" target="_blank">Doc</a></p>
<p><img src="http://forsigner.com/images/fexo/mobile.png?v=1" alt="screenshot-1"><br><img src="http://forsigner.com/images/fexo/fexo-1.png?v=1" alt="screenshot-1"><br><img src="http://forsigner.com/images/fexo/fexo-2.png?v1" alt="screenshot-2"></p>
